description:
Jonathan Ferguson, a weapons expert and Keeper of Firearms & Artillery at the Royal Armouries, breaks down more of the weaponry of Warhammer 40,000: Space Marine, including the iconic Boltgun, the Melta Gun, and the Vengeance Launcher.

00:00 - Opening
00:34 - Bolt Pistol
02:15 - Bolter
04:45 - Heavy Bolter
06:05 - Stalker Bolter
07:38 - Storm Bolter
09:38 - Lascannon
11:18 - Melta Gun
12:47 - Plasma Pistol
14:24 - Vengeance Launcher
15:45 - Ork Weapons

In the latest video in the Firearm Expert Reacts series, Jonathan Ferguson--a weapons expert and Keeper of Firearms & Artillery at the Royal Armouries--breaks down the guns of Warhammer 40,000: Space Marine and compares them to their potential real-life counterparts.

Firearms Expert Reacts playlist - https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=y4T78VQoWUs&list=PLpg6WLs8kxGMgYb13XjPgOKbm5O-CDq7R

If you're interested in seeing more of Jonathan's work, you can check out more from the Royal Armouries right here. - https://www.youtube.com/user/Royal
title: Firearms Expert Reacts To Warhammer 40K: Space Marine’s Guns
